{
  "stem": "19690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a cook who was also a resistance fighter who was our contact.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He saw to everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few weeks after we were there, word came down that everybody who was under 16 had to leave.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he hid a bunch of them in the coal bins in the basement and in the water tanks on the roof.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These all had cisterns on the roof to supply water for the building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they stayed there for about two or three days while the Germans were looking for them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the heat was off, he smuggled these people out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later on his milk cart that he took out every morning to get milk and groceries for the kitchen, he would take their suitcases out gradually so that their belongings would disappear, too.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This happened twice, once for everybody up to 16, then once for everybody above 14.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was 13 at the time, so I was still relatively lucky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a diphtheria scare, I spent some time in the hospital getting shots, and then came back to the hotel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And finally in October, we were sent to the children's homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were put on trains and taken to Toulouse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In Toulouse, we were split up into the five camps in the area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was with several others taken to Chateau [NON-ENGLISH], which is near [NON-ENGLISH] in the [NON-ENGLISH] province of France.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have been back there since.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in fact, it was also the camp-- the children's home-- where Klaus [NON-ENGLISH] was when he was a little boy and was separated from his father.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I found this out just recently when I saw-- when I found his book at the Holocaust Museum in Washington.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was a place where I was exceedingly happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
